  "text": "For each subject and each axial slice, the SC was semi-automatically segmented ( Fig. 1a , step 1) using the PropSeg function from the Spinal Cord Toolbox [CITATION_1] . Segmentations of the GM, the WM and the central canal were performed manually for each individual dataset by the same operator using the viewer module of the FSL package (FSL v4.1.3, FMRIB, Oxford, UK) ( Fig. 1a , step 2). When visible, anterior fissure and posterior septum were excluded from WM segmentation.",
